title: Ala Da De Qimiao Shijie
synopsis: The story takes place on the present earth. There is a forest not far from the city. There is a lush and magical tree in the forest. There are a group of kind and brave green elves living in the tree. They have their own names. ——The long-winded but caring Elf Elders, the brave and strong Alpha, the kind and clever boy, the naughty and clever Mumu, the beautiful and intelligent Ami and the innocent and lovely Nini, they together form the happy green elves family . Every green elf has a healthy, positive, and constantly upward mentality. They also have joy, anger, sorrow, and joy like children. They have to learn, like to play, and are innocent and naughty. The difference is that green elf has wings to fly, superpowers and battle magic. (translated from )
